data.description: This lovely ranch home in highly desired Windsor, with no HOA or Metro Tax is perfect for the first-time home buyer!  It's on a corner lot in a quiet neighborhood with minimal traffic.  It has an inviting great room with hardwood oak flooring, a bay window and ceiling fan.  All appliances stay in the nicely sized eat-in kitchen which has oak cabinets, a pantry and a sliding door to the backyard.  This spacious primary bedroom is sure to please with its large walk-in closet, ceiling fan, and ensuite  3/4 bath.  Two more bedrooms plus a full bath are also found on the main floor.  A good portion of the inside of this home has been freshly painted.  The basement is great for storage, and is a blank slate to be finished as you desire.  Its lot is complimented with mature trees, a xeriscaped front yard which has a sprinkler system and a minimal amount of grass, and the back yard is mostly fenced.  Location is top notch, being within walking distance to Mountain View Elementary and the library, plus is only minutes away from entertainment, breweries, restaurants, and grocery.  Make this home with so much to offer yours today!
